                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "劇情預告-「人間至味」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/7caca68a51e7ac54570df4a2b11efd75_5586238987955251157.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2021年10月2日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "年歲一箸，山海一壺。閱古話今，幾度春秋。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "炊煙喜樂，柴米朝暮。纖雲逐月，塵世繫舟。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "劇情預告-「神女劈觀」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/c7c89b91a563baec537660234250afd6_8576062249495287418.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年1月6日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "道仙緣奇談，物是人非，疏卻千絲怨愁。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "歌巾幗英姿，再添新話，重入萬家燈火。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "飛彩鐫流年活動過場動畫「歲華流彩」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/21da0584c68f1fc3b166df576240cd2c_8049595838719453616.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年1月31日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "火樹銀花，散漫天飛星，迎萬象似錦。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "榮輝彩華，凝萬千心願，祝山月常新。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "角色展示-「瑤瑤：仙桂瑩澈」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/2913894fe26a62b006d8856ba04c7c20_9178647630462287109.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2023年1月16日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "瑤瑤對其他人的關心，可不會因為對方的身分有所改變。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "無論是師父、長輩，還是玩伴、過客，都有機會體驗到她的無微不至。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "請不要嫌棄瑤瑤的多話，畢竟她心中飽含的熱忱關懷，可能比她說的話還要多呢。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "磬弦奏華夜活動過場動畫-「虹歌燈宴」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/302104f08566c84d9702f4868938fffe_1075261458542669279.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2023年1月21日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "新歲新象，摯友摯願。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "在這華彩映照的夜晚，璃月港內不止有霄燈，還有融匯萬籟的仙樂。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "劇情預告-「餘音縈心」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/7cca2be08e92fd6268d1fe9478f14c74_7420650454029978282.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2023年1月21日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "過眼雲煙，浮萍無根。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "涓涓行水，渺渺滌塵。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "風物集短片-璃月篇",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/e38c7b9711115465e57bdb8971784e4f_8655281959375010967.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2023年6月21日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "山石奇景，巍巍難撼。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "商港熙榮，閱盡千帆。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
